message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely category as the paper deals with audio scene separation, which is a core task in computer audition. Other likely categories could be cs.SI (signal processing), cs.LG (machine learning), cs.SY (systems and control), and cs.CV (computer vision) as the paper uses deep networks and primitive cues to train a network on a large set of unlabeled music recordings from YouTube to separate vocals from accompaniment.
